unitRoutes.use(resolveTenant, optionalAuth, requireTenant);
// Remove resolveTenant from the route-level middleware since it's on the router now
```

This ensures ALL unit routes 400-error without a tenant slug.

### Step 3 — Apply to projects route
**File:** `server/src/routes/projects.routes.ts`

Same pattern:
```typescript
