## PLAN 08 — Create Documents Storage Bucket Migration
**Severity:** 🟠 High | **Owner:** DB / DevOps | **Est:** 30min

### Problem
`pdf.service.ts` uploads to `documents` bucket; no migration creates this bucket. Receipts and document uploads silently fail with storage errors.

### New file
