// Use `count` instead of `data?.count ?? 0`
```

### ✅ Definition of Done
- [ ] New notification badge appears within ~1s of server inserting a notification for that user
- [ ] No polling fallback needed for bell (Realtime handles it); 60s poll remains as backup
- [ ] Channel properly unsubscribed on component unmount

